original_title: Jazz Icons: The Svend Asmussen Quartet
overview: In this live concert recording, legendary jazz violinist Svend Asmussen performs alongside Kenny Drew, Niel Henning orsted Pedersen and Ed Thigpen. This masterful quartet performs a variety of jazz classics at the Club Montmartre in Copenhagen, Denmark.
title: Jazz Icons: The Svend Asmussen Quartet
